      "path": "/pages/blogs/blog-4.html",
      "title": "10 Signs It's Time to Redesign Your Website in 2026 (+ Full Redesign Checklist) | Webx Design Studio",
      "meta": "Discover 10 clear signs your website needs a redesign in 2026, with a practical checklist covering UX, SEO, performance, and conversion optimization.",
      "displayName": "Blog 4",
      "summary": "blogs page • 7 editable sections",
      "templateStart": "<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n<head>\r\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\r\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\r\n\r\n<title>10 Signs It's Time to Redesign Your Website in 2026 (+ Full Redesign Checklist) | Webx Design Studio</title>\r\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Discover 10 clear signs your website needs a redesign in 2026, with a practical checklist covering UX, SEO, performance, and conversion optimization.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\" />\r\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Webx Design Studio\" />\r\n<meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#ff6b00\" />\r\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"website redesign 2026, when to redesign website, website redesign checklist\" />\r\n\r\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://webxds.com/pages/blogs/blog-4.html\" />\r\n\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"10 Signs It's Time to Redesign Your Website in 2026 (+ Full Redesign Checklist)\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Discover 10 clear signs your website needs a redesign in 2026, with a practical checklist covering UX, SEO, performance, and conversion optimization.\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://webxds.com/pages/blogs/blog-4.html\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://webxds.com/assets/images/blogs/blog-img-4.png\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image:alt\" content=\"10 Signs Website Redesign Needed in 2026 - Webx Design Studio\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Webx Design Studio\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_IN\" />\r\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2026-02-18\" />\r\n<meta property=\"article:author\" content=\"Webx Design Studio\" />\r\n<meta property=\"article:section\" content=\"UX/UI Design\" />\r\n<meta property=\"article:tag\" content=\"website redesign 2026\" />\r\n<meta property=\"article:tag\" content=\"when to redesign website\" />\r\n<meta property=\"article:tag\" content=\"website redesign checklist\" />\r\n\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"10 Signs It's Time to Redesign Your Website in 2026 (+ Full Redesign Checklist)\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Discover 10 clear signs your website needs a redesign in 2026, with a practical checklist covering UX, SEO, performance, and conversion optimization.\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://webxds.com/assets/images/blogs/blog-img-4.png\" />\r\n<meta name=\"twitter:image:alt\" content=\"10 Signs Website Redesign Needed in 2026 - Webx Design Studio\" />\r\n\r\n<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/assets/images/icons/favicon.png\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" />\r\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/assets/images/icons/favicon-180.png\" sizes=\"180x180\" />\r\n<link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/manifest.json\" />\r\n\r\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\" />\r\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin />\r\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\" />\r\n\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/style.css\" />\r\n<link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/assets/images/hero/hero-mockup.jpg\" as=\"image\" />\r\n\r\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\r\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\r\n  \"headline\": \"10 Signs It's Time to Redesign Your Website in 2026 (+ Full Redesign Checklist)\",\r\n  \"description\": \"Discover 10 clear signs your website needs a redesign in 2026, with a practical checklist covering UX, SEO, performance, and conversion optimization.\",\r\n  \"image\": \"https://webxds.com/assets/images/blogs/blog-i